  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Arrange items to fit them into your inventory:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275100/extras/991d8e872f972c6e4acf747824878bb3.poster.avif?t=1747003569\" width=616 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275100/extras/991d8e872f972c6e4acf747824878bb3.webm?t=1747003569\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275100/extras/991d8e872f972c6e4acf747824878bb3.mp4?t=1747003569\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Examine items to gather more information:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275100/extras/494819fe9fb55ea2f49a2f70f7a8126f.poster.avif?t=1747003569\" width=616 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275100/extras/494819fe9fb55ea2f49a2f70f7a8126f.webm?t=1747003569\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275100/extras/494819fe9fb55ea2f49a2f70f7a8126f.mp4?t=1747003569\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Reload your weapons:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2275100/extras/86c8247e5139b082dbf054320b90bc32.poster.avif?t=1747003569\" width=616 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/a